{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/extras/bunner.gif?t=1727873798\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/extras/gif_store_444\u0445250.gif?t=1727873798\" /><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u00a0 \u00a0Battle of Arachnidia Demo</strong> is an addictive top-down arcade shooter, a modern interpretation of classic arcade games. The game is set in a battle mech battles with hordes of spider-robot warriors. Your task is to defend your base by exterminating all enemies, making your way through all sorts of tactical solutions, improving your robot and using various power-ups to help in the fight. The demo includes five levels of the game that will allow you to really get a feel for the gameplay and mechanics of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/extras/keyfeaturesrus_eng.png?t=1727873798\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> a lot of different levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> different levels with unique abilities of the enemy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> a system of easily obtaining bonuses that help repel attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> the level raising system of the individual fighting robot makes it more destructive<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/extras/developers_eng.png?t=1727873798\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2>The game was completely developed by one person - Volodymyr Krysenko, as a tribute to classic arcade games.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=17278